    "title": "What Market-Based Instrument Are You?",
    "subtitle": "A BuzzFeed-style vibe check for the neoliberal valuation of nature.",
    "intro": "Market-based instruments promise to save the planet by pricing it. Find out which one you are!",
    "resultLabel": "Your market-based instrument"
  },
